results.Name: Trigun: The Complete Series
results.Synopsis: To bounty hunters in this animated adventure series, Vash the Stampede is an outlaw with a massive price on his head. But to Meryl Stryfe and Milly Thompson of the Bernardelli Insurance Society, Vash is a walking disaster who has cost the company a fortune. On a distant, deserted planet that resembles America's Old West, Vash wanders from town to town, with Meryl and Milly in pursuit trying to minimize the destruction.
results.ShortSynopsis: An outlaw named Vash the Stampede -- who has a massive price on his head -- wanders from town to town on a deserted planet that resembles the Wild West.

results.Name: Firefly: The Complete Series
results.Synopsis: Set almost 500 years in the future, this short-lived but much-loved TV series follows the adventures of the ragtag crew of the transport spaceship &NFi;Serenity&NFi_;, who view no job as too small, too dirty or too close to the line of illegality.
results.ShortSynopsis: Set almost 500 years in the future, this short-lived but much-loved series follows the adventures of the ragtag crew of the spaceship Serenity.

results.Name: Scarred: Season 1
results.Synopsis: Papa Roach front man Jacoby Shaddix hosts this MTV series that showcases amateur video footage of the most gruesomely punishing crashes, spills, wipeouts and accidents experienced by extreme sports athletes and other would-be daredevils. With graphic testimonials to accompany the horrific clips, this Internet-inspired series makes for agonizing -- though strangely compelling -- viewing. Ouch!

results.Name: Mr. Meaty: Season 1
results.Synopsis: The result of a collection of animated shorts, this series tells the story of Josh and Parker, two hapless teenagers who work together at their local food court's Mr. Meaty burger franchise but dream about one day having successful Hollywood careers. While Josh dislikes his job and struggles to get girls to notice him, Parker enjoys his post as fry cook and happily embraces his inner (and outer) geek.
results.ShortSynopsis: The result of a collection of animated shorts, this series tells the story of Josh and Parker, two hapless teenagers who work together at their local food court's Mr. Meaty burger franchise but dream about one day having successful Hollywood careers.

results.Name: Making Fiends: Season 1
results.Synopsis: Charlotte, a young girl new to the town of Clumberg, meets and is determined to befriend Vendatta, a very creepy student who, unfortunately, has it in for lovable Charlotte. The show's fresh look and feel, unusual creatures, cutting-edge animation and off-beat humor, along with Charlotte's unflappable, contagious charm, make this Nickelodeon animated series irresistible to children and adults alike.
results.ShortSynopsis: Charlotte, a young girl new to the town of Clumberg, meets and is determined to befriend Vendatta, a very creepy student who, unfortunately, has it in for lovable Charlotte.

results.Name: Rad
results.Synopsis: Cru Jones (Bill Allen), a rising talent on the BMX track, faces an uphill climb as he gears up for the important Helltrack race. He must contend with a shady sponsor who changes the rules at the last minute, and champion rider Bart Taylor (Bart Conner) is hoping for an easy victory. And when Cru realizes that the race falls on the same day as an important school test, he must decide whether bikes or books will determine his future.
results.ShortSynopsis: A rising talent on the BMX circuit faces an uphill climb as he gears up for a vital race while contending with a shady sponsor who changes the rules.

results.Name: Good Eats: Season 1
results.Synopsis: In the premiere season of this long-running Food Network show, culinary expert Alton Brown leads you on a funny and informative journey into the kitchen and beyond, irreverently explaining the science behind the elements of food preparation. Shedding light on the whys of cooking as well as the how-tos, Brown turns his attention to searing the perfect steak, baking biscuits, grilling salmon, making homemade ice cream and more.
results.ShortSynopsis: Culinary expert Alton Brown leads you on a funny and informative journey into the kitchen, irreverently explaining the science of food preparation.

results.Name: King Lines
results.Synopsis: Join celebrated pro athlete Chris Sharma -- regarded as the world's greatest rock climber -- as he travels from one end of the globe to the other in search of the planet's most awe-inspiring climbs. Filmed in high definition, this Emmy-winning film follows Sharma as he tackles one seemingly impossible challenge after another, from the 70-foot arch rising off the coast of Mallorca to an ominous overhanging rock face in Ceuse, France.
results.ShortSynopsis: Join celebrated pro athlete Chris Sharma -- regarded as the world's greatest rock climber -- as he travels from one end of the globe to the other in search of the planet's most awe-inspiring climbs.

results.Name: The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King: Extended Edition
results.ShortName: LOTR: Return of the King: Extended Ed.
results.Synopsis: In the Oscar-winning final installment of the Lord of the Rings trilogy, Aragorn (Viggo Mortensen) is revealed as the heir to the ancient kings as he, Gandalf (Ian McKellen) and the other members of the broken fellowship struggle to save Gondor from Sauron's forces. Meanwhile, Frodo (Elijah Wood) and Sam (Sean Astin) bring the ring into Mordor, the dark lord's realm. This extended version adds 50 minutes of footage to the theatrical cut.
results.ShortSynopsis: In the final installment of the trilogy, Aragorn is revealed as heir to the ancient kings as he, Gandalf and the fellowship struggle to save Gondor.

results.Name: Rush: Working Men
results.Synopsis: Watch as legendary rock band Rush belts out their greatest hits in this live concert compilation, which features such popular tracks as "Tom Sawyer," "Limelight," "The Spirit of Radio" and "Closer to the Heart." Alternating between clips from their popular concert recordings R30, Rush in Rio and Snakes & Arrows Live, this outstanding set showcases band members Geddy Lee, Alex Lifeson and Neil Peart in truly fine form.
results.ShortSynopsis: Watch as legendary rock band Rush belts out their greatest hits in this live concert compilation, which features such popular tracks as "Tom Sawyer," "Limelight," "The Spirit of Radio" and "Closer to the Heart."

results.Name: Phish 3D
results.Synopsis: The wildly popular and eclectic band Phish storms the screen in a 2009 3-D concert experience filmed in front of 40,000 enthusiastic fans during a three-day, multifestival event held in Southern California. One of Phish's most intriguing innovations -- the musical costume -- is documented with their rollicking recreation of the entire Rolling Stones album "Exile on Main St." Excerpts from a full-length acoustic set are also featured.
results.ShortSynopsis: The wildly popular and eclectic band Phish storms the screen in a 2009 3-D concert experience filmed in front of 40,000 enthusiastic fans during a three-day, multifestival event held in Southern California.

results.Name: Sea Prince and the Fire Child
results.ShortName: Sea Prince and the Fire Child
results.Synopsis: Sanrio (Hello Kitty) produced this animated classic about an affair between Prince Sirius, the ocean king's son, and Hyperia, the fire queen's daughter -- a forbidden passion that rocks longstanding conflict between water sprites and fire fairies. In their world, they can never be together. But a shared life on a distant star is possible if they can make it to the hill of Elysium and pluck a magical flower during the next solar eclipse.
results.ShortSynopsis: Sanrio (Hello Kitty) produced this animated classic about an affair between Prince Sirius, the ocean king's son, and Hyperia, the fire queen's daughter -- a forbidden passion that rocks longstanding conflict between water sprites and fire fairies.

results.Name: Gintama: The Movie
results.Synopsis: Based on Hideaki Sorachi's popular manga and the animated TV series that followed, this feature-length anime follows the adventures of aging samurai Gintoki in medieval Tokyo -- then known as Edo -- which has been invaded by aliens. Since only a few vestiges of Japanese culture remain, it's up to Gintoki to carry the torch and keep the peace, with help from his two young interns -- a gawky teenage boy and a rough-and-tumble alien girl.
results.ShortSynopsis: Based on Hideaki Sorachi's popular manga and the animated TV series that followed, this feature-length anime follows the adventures of aging samurai Gintoki in medieval Tokyo -- then known as Edo -- which has been invaded by aliens.

results.Name: Slayer: Live Intrusion
results.Synopsis: Hell hath no fury like the spectacle of Slayer shredding onstage, and this long-out-of-print concert film from the 1995 Divine Intervention tour witnesses the metal aggressors at their bludgeoning best. Filmed at the Mesa Amphitheatre in Arizona, the show's set list includes "Raining Blood," "War Ensemble," "Angel of Death" and Venom's "Witching Hour," with interview clips and glimpses backstage adding fuel to the fire.
results.ShortSynopsis: Hell hath no fury like the spectacle of Slayer shredding onstage, and this long-out-of-print concert film from the 1995 Divine Intervention tour witnesses the metal aggressors at their bludgeoning best.

results.Name: For Liberty: How the Ron Paul Revolution Watered the Withered Tree of Liberty
results.Synopsis: Political maverick and 2008 presidential candidate Ron Paul was a little-known member of the House of Representatives before his startling policy principles caught fire with the American public and shook up the political establishment. This film chronicles the politico's journey, capturing the electric excitement of Paul's national campaign while chronicling its lasting impact on the U.S. electoral landscape.
results.ShortSynopsis: Political maverick and 2008 presidential candidate Ron Paul was a little-known member of the House of Representatives before his startling policy principles caught fire with the American public and shook up the political establishment.

results.Name: Tsubasa: Tokyo Revelations & Spring Thunder Chronicle
results.Synopsis: Traveling across countless worlds, Sakura, Syaoran, Fai and Kurogane continue their quest to gather the feathers that hold the key to Sakura's memories -- and her soul -- in this collection of episodes from the intricately plotted anime series. In "Tokyo Revelations," the group discovers the villain responsible for scattering Sakura's feathers, while "Spring Thunder Chronicle" sees Syaoran facing off against a clone version of himself.
results.ShortSynopsis: Traveling across countless worlds, Sakura, Syaoran, Fai and Kurogane continue their quest to gather the feathers that hold the key to Sakura's memories -- and her soul -- in this collection of episodes from the intricately plotted anime series.

results.Name: Adventure Time: My Two Favorite People
results.ShortName: Adventure Time: My Two Favorite People
results.Synopsis: Finn is a 12-year-old boy who counts on the companionship of his buddy Jake, a dog with magical powers. Together the thrill-seeking duo seeks adventure in the surreal land of Ooo, meeting all manner of crazy creatures along the way. A typical day for the pair may include rescuing princesses and people in need, battling monsters or delving into dungeons. Jeremy Shada and John Di Maggio are among the voice actors for this animated series.
results.ShortSynopsis: Finn is a 12-year-old boy who counts on the companionship of his buddy Jake, a dog with magical powers. Together the thrill-seeking duo seeks adventure in the surreal land of Ooo, meeting all manner of crazy creatures along the way.

results.Name: Celtic Thunder: Heritage
results.Synopsis: Ensemble singing sensation Celtic Thunder showcase the traditional music of Ireland in this concert video, filmed live during the group's "Heritage" tour and featuring tunes such as "My Love Is Like a Red, Red Rose" and "Whiskey in the Jar." The lads also bring their unique blend of solos, group numbers and dramatic stage choreography to "Ireland's Call," "Home from the Sea," "Black is the Colour" and other tunes.
results.ShortSynopsis: Ensemble singing sensation Celtic Thunder showcase the traditional music of Ireland in this concert video, filmed live during the group's "Heritage" tour and featuring tunes such as "My Love Is Like a Red, Red Rose" and "Whiskey in the Jar."

results.Name: Lost Boy: The Next Chapter
results.Synopsis: In this biographical portrait, California-based pastor Greg Laurie tells the story of how he came to find God in his own words, tracing his transformation to a life-changing encounter with a group of young Christians in high school. Since that day, he's gone on to spread the word to thousands of others through his Harvest Christian Fellowship mega-church as well as the church's Harvest Crusades ministry.
results.ShortSynopsis: In this biographical portrait, California-based pastor Greg Laurie tells the story of how he came to find God in his own words, tracing his transformation to a life-changing encounter with a group of young Christians in high school.

results.Name: Ben Bailey: Road Rage and Accidental Ornithology
results.ShortName: Ben Bailey: Road Rage and Accidental...
results.Synopsis: Former host of the Emmy-winning game show "Cash Cab," Ben Bailey takes his talent to the stage in a hilarious and often surreal live Comedy Central performance where he takes on subjects ranging from owls to the insanity of New York traffic.
results.ShortSynopsis: Former host of the Emmy-winning game show "Cash Cab," Ben Bailey takes his talent to the stage in a hilarious and often surreal live Comedy Central performance where he takes on subjects ranging from owls to the insanity of New York traffic.

results.Name: Secret Garden
results.Synopsis: Fate works in mysterious ways in this Korean dramedy when a high-powered businessman and a self-made stuntwoman swap bodies indefinitely, forcing each to see the world through a fresh new set of eyes.
results.ShortSynopsis: Fate works in mysterious ways in this Korean dramedy when a high-powered businessman and a self-made stuntwoman swap bodies indefinitely, forcing each to see the world through a fresh new set of eyes.

results.Name: Bold Native
results.Synopsis: Using the tried-and-true road movie format to send a strong social message about the humane treatment of animals -- including those used for industrial farming -- this drama focuses on the plight of an animal rights activist wanted for terrorism.
results.ShortSynopsis: Using the tried-and-true road movie format to send a strong social message about the humane treatment of animals -- including those used for industrial farming -- this drama focuses on the plight of an animal rights activist wanted for terrorism.

results.Name: Pokemon Zoroark: Master of Illusions
results.Synopsis: In this anime film, Ash and Pikachu visit Crown City for the Pokémon Baccer World Cup and make friends with Zorua, a curious new Pokémon. But soon the entire city is threatened with destruction by the mysterious and powerful Pokémon Zoroark.
results.ShortSynopsis: In this anime film, Ash and Pikachu visit Crown City just as it is threatened with destruction by the mysterious and powerful Pokémon Zoroark.

results.Name: WWE: Randy Orton: The Evolution of a Predator: Vol. 1
results.ShortName: The Evolution of a Predator: Vol. 1
results.Synopsis: Wrestling champ Randy Orton, a legendary fixture in the WWE since 2002, recalls all the wild chapters of his career in this full-length interview. The Viper speaks frankly about finding a personal sense of destiny and battling through injuries.
results.ShortSynopsis: Wrestling champ Randy Orton, a legendary fixture in the WWE since 2002, recalls all the wild chapters of his career in this full-length interview.

results.Name: K-ON!: Vol. 1
results.Synopsis: This anime series follows Yui Hirasawa into high school, where she can't find a club to her liking until she discovers the Light Music Club. Though lacking musical experience, Yui vows to learn to play guitar so she can join the club's rock band.
results.ShortSynopsis: This anime series follows Yui Hirasawa into high school, where she can't find a club to her liking until she discovers the Light Music Club.

results.Name: Red vs. Blue: Season 9
results.Synopsis: This lighthearted machinima series splits its ninth season into two divergent storylines that provide both a prequel and a sequel to the action. In the process, the mysteries of Project Freelancer are revealed.
results.ShortSynopsis: This lighthearted machinima series splits its ninth season into two divergent storylines that provide both a prequel and a sequel to the action.

results.Name: Hetalia: Paint It, White
results.Synopsis: In this feature-length animated film inspired by the hit anime series, Allied and Axis characters must put aside their hostility in order to confront an onslaught of aliens who are painting the entire Earth, turning it into a vast white wasteland.
results.ShortSynopsis: Allied and Axis characters must join forces to confront aliens who are painting the entire Earth, turning it into a vast white wasteland.

results.Name: Diary of a Wimpy Kid: Dog Days
results.ShortName: Diary of a Wimpy Kid: Dog Days
results.Synopsis: Based on the hit children's book, this comedy follows misfit Greg Heffley and his pal Rowley Jefferson as their summer vacation disintegrates into one wild misadventure after another, including a disastrous attempt to start a lawn-mowing business.
results.ShortSynopsis: Greg Heffley's summer vacation disintegrates into one misadventure after another, including a disastrous attempt to start a lawn-mowing business.

results.Name: Naruto Shippuden: Vol. 25
results.Synopsis: The epic adventures continue in these episodes from the hit anime series that follows the exploits of young ninja Naruto, who has just returned home from a years-long training mission with legendary warrior Jiraiya. Vol. 25 contains episodes 101-104.
results.ShortSynopsis: The epic adventures continue in these episodes from the hit anime series that follows the exploits of young ninja Naruto, who has just returned home from a years-long training mission with legendary warrior Jiraiya. Vol. 25 contains episodes 101-104.

results.Name: Naruto Shippuden: Vol. 26
results.Synopsis: The epic adventures continue in these episodes from the hit anime series that follows the exploits of young ninja Naruto, who has just returned home from a years-long training mission with legendary warrior Jiraiya. Vol. 26 contains episodes 105-108.
results.ShortSynopsis: The epic adventures continue in these episodes from the hit anime series that follows the exploits of young ninja Naruto, who has just returned home from a years-long training mission with legendary warrior Jiraiya. Vol. 26 contains episodes 105-108.

results.Name: My Little Pony: Friendship Is Magic: Ponyville Chronicle
results.ShortName: My Little Pony: Friendship Is Magic
results.Synopsis: This enchanting animated show follows the adventures of Twilight Sparkle, a unicorn pony sent by Princess Celestia to Ponyville, where she and her pals Fluttershy, Applejack, Rarity, Pinkie Pie and Rainbow Dash learn all about being true friends.
results.ShortSynopsis: This enchanting animated show follows the adventures of Twilight Sparkle, a unicorn pony sent to Ponyville to learn all about being a true friend.

results.Name: Zeitgeist: Moving Forward
results.Synopsis: This compelling documentary examines the current state of the global socioeconomic monetary paradigm and concludes that we need to transition to a new resource-based economy for our continued human and social survival.
results.ShortSynopsis: This documentary examines the state of the global socioeconomic monetary paradigm, concluding that we need to move to a new resource-based economy.

results.Name: Zeitgeist: Addendum
results.Synopsis: Continuing the discussion from Zeitgeist: The Movie about the controversial links between religion and the financial markets, this documentary explores the causes of social corruption and puts forth a solution based on human alignment with nature.
results.ShortSynopsis: Continuing the discussion from Zeitgeist: The Movie about the controversial links between religion and the financial markets, this documentary explores the causes of social corruption and puts forth a solution based on human alignment with nature.

results.Name: Adventure Time: It Came From the Nightosphere
results.Synopsis: Wannabe hero Finn and his magical dog Jake go on exciting adventures in the curious Land of Ooo. Along the way, they interact with the wife-seeking Ice King, rocker chick Marceline, cloudlike Lumpy Space Princess and other offbeat characters.
results.ShortSynopsis: Wannabe hero Finn and his magical dog Jake go on adventures in the Land of Ooo, where they interact with the Ice King and other offbeat characters.

results.Name: Naruto Shippuden: Vol. 28
results.Synopsis: The epic adventures continue in these episodes from the hit anime series that follows the exploits of young ninja Naruto, who has just returned home from a years-long training mission with legendary warrior Jiraiya. Vol. 28 contains episodes 113-117.
results.ShortSynopsis: The epic adventures continue in these episodes from the hit anime series that follows the exploits of young ninja Naruto, who has just returned home from a years-long training mission with legendary warrior Jiraiya. Vol.

results.Name: Naruto Shippuden: Vol. 30
results.Synopsis: The epic adventures continue in these episodes from the hit anime series that follows the exploits of young ninja Naruto, who has just returned home from a years-long training mission with legendary warrior Jiraiya. Vol. 30 contains episodes 123-126.
results.ShortSynopsis: The epic adventures continue in these episodes from the hit anime series that follows the exploits of young ninja Naruto, who has just returned home from a years-long training mission with legendary warrior Jiraiya. Vol.

results.Name: Hetalia: Axis Powers: Season 2
results.Synopsis: With a loose nod to history (and a smattering of ethnic stereotypes), this inventive anime personifies the Axis powers that we all know from World War II -- Italy, Germany and Japan -- and re-imagines them as super-cute boys.
results.ShortSynopsis: With a loose nod to history, this inventive anime personifies the Axis powers that we all know from World War II and re-imagines them as cute boys.

results.Name: Birdy the Mighty: Decode: Part 2
results.Synopsis: Birdy is thrown back into duty as an intergalactic federation investigator tracking down a group of escaped criminal aliens hiding out on Earth -- all while she maintains her celebrity alter ego and as Tsutomu continues to inhabit Birdy's body.
results.ShortSynopsis: Birdy is thrown back into duty as an intergalactic federation investigator tracking down a group of escaped criminal aliens hiding out on Earth.

results.Name: Storm Chasers: Season 2
results.Synopsis: The world's top storm chasers return to Tornado Alley, now armed to get closer than ever to America's deadly twisters.  Meteorologist Reed Timmer, Imax filmmaker Sean Casey and weather engineer Tim Samaras battle the weather to get images and data.
results.ShortSynopsis: The world's top storm chasers return to Tornado Alley, now armed to get closer than ever to America's deadly twisters. Meteorologist Reed Timmer, Imax filmmaker Sean Casey and weather engineer Tim Samaras battle the weather to get images and data.

results.Name: Big Time Rush: Season 1: Vol. 2
results.Synopsis: These first-season episodes from the lighthearted musical TV series follow the further adventures of four Minnesota lads (played by Kendall Schmidt, Carlos Pena, Logan Henderson and James Maslow) who move to Los Angeles with dreams of making their vocal group, Big Time Rush, the next hot boy band. Just as their career is set to take off, the boys and their demanding manager Gustavo Rocque (Stephen Kramer Glickman) come face-to-face with failure.
results.ShortSynopsis: These first-season episodes from the lighthearted musical TV series follow the further adventures of four Minnesota lads who move to Los Angeles with dreams of making their vocal group, Big Time Rush, the next hot boy band.

results.Name: How the Universe Works
results.Synopsis: Host Mike Rowe brings viewers on an enlightening tour of our current cosmic knowledge in this miniseries that starts with the Big Bang and covers alien galaxies and solar systems, as well as the space-shattering properties of a supernova event.
results.ShortSynopsis: Host Mike Rowe brings viewers on an enlightening tour of our current cosmic knowledge in this miniseries that starts with the Big Bang and covers alien galaxies and solar systems, as well as the space-shattering properties of a supernova event.

results.Name: Storm Chasers: Season 3
results.Synopsis: The third season of this Discovery Channel reality series finds intrepid storm chasers Reed Timmer, Sean Casey and Tim Samaras running down more of Mother Nature's deadliest twisters to see what makes them tick.
results.ShortSynopsis: The third season of this Discovery Channel reality series finds intrepid storm chasers Reed Timmer, Sean Casey and Tim Samaras running down more of Mother Nature's deadliest twisters to see what makes them tick.

results.Name: You Are Beautiful
results.Synopsis: As her twin brother recovers from plastic surgery, a young woman takes his place in a boy band. At first, the group members are cold to her, but she soon wins the heart of her bandmates and fans, all the while searching for her long-lost mother.
results.ShortSynopsis: As her twin brother recovers from plastic surgery, a young woman takes his place in a boy band. At first, the group members are cold to her, but she soon wins the heart of her bandmates and fans, all the while searching for her long-lost mother.

results.Name: Rosario + Vampire: Season 1
results.Synopsis: When Tsukune accidentally enrolls in a school for monsters disguised as humans, he must hide the fact that he's really human or risk losing his life. After falling for cute vampire Moka, he decides it's worth the risk to stay.
results.ShortSynopsis: When Tsukune accidentally enrolls in a school for monsters disguised as humans, he must hide the fact that he's really human or risk losing his life.

results.Name: Dead Like Me: Season 2
results.Synopsis: In her second year as a not-so-grim reaper, George (Ellen Muth) decides it's time to have some fun and act her age, which includes meeting guys and falling in love -- or at least in lust -- just as her still-alive parents are on the brink of divorce. In the meantime, her sister (Britt McKillip) grapples with George's death, and her co-workers continue to play out their individual dramas and high jinks, forever trying to exorcise their demons.
results.ShortSynopsis: In her second season as a not-so-grim reaper, George decides it's time to have fun and act her age -- which includes meeting guys and falling in love.
